WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: kPqUX6Bpb-c

NOTE Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.959
Her followers see Her as a great spiritual leader,

00:00:02.125 --> 00:00:05.041
capable of curing all ills, even cancer.

00:00:05.291 --> 00:00:07.583
Well, these are the sort of claims you’ve probably heard before

00:00:07.792 --> 00:00:09.458
from many so-called gurus,

00:00:09.667 --> 00:00:12.041
but for Her fast expanding group of disciples

00:00:12.250 --> 00:00:14.542
Mataji Nirmala Devi is different.

00:00:14.750 --> 00:00:17.750
Tonight She brings Her message to a public meeting in Exeter.

00:00:17.959 --> 00:00:20.083
REPORTER: Mataji, the world of healing and gurus

00:00:20.291 --> 00:00:22.792
is full of frauds and charlatans.

00:00:23.083 --> 00:00:25.375
Do you accept that many people might be skeptical about Your claims?

00:00:25.583 --> 00:00:26.917
SHRI MATAJI: Of course they should be.

00:00:27.083 --> 00:00:29.000
Why they are not I don’t understand, you see.

00:00:29.250 --> 00:00:32.750
You must use your brains and reach right conclusions.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Why are you seeking, what are you seeking

00:00:35.208 --> 00:00:36.667
and whom are you going to.

00:00:36.875 --> 00:00:38.458
Those people who charge you money

00:00:38.667 --> 00:00:41.583
and live like parasites on you cannot be your gurus, you see,

00:00:41.792 --> 00:00:43.542
they are people without any self-respect.

00:00:43.750 --> 00:00:45.208
REPORTER: You don’t charge any money at all?

00:00:45.417 --> 00:00:48.000
SHRI MATAJI: Not at all. I mean, how can I charge money for this,

00:00:48.208 --> 00:00:51.583
is Love, Love of God. How can I charge money for that?

00:00:51.834 --> 00:00:54.208
REPORTER: It’s claimed that even viewers of an interview such as this

00:00:54.417 --> 00:00:56.375
just by looking at Your picture on the television screen

00:00:56.583 --> 00:00:58.834
can receive some sort of physical manifestation

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:00.417
of Your power. Now, how does that work?

00:01:00.625 --> 00:01:02.166
SHRI MATAJI: Yes. By,  just if they put their hands

00:01:02.375 --> 00:01:04.166
towards Me like this even now,

00:01:04.375 --> 00:01:07.667
they can feel a cool breeze flowing into their hands.

00:01:07.875 --> 00:01:10.917
So many might feel, as they felt it in Hong Kong,

00:01:11.125 --> 00:01:14.125
but if you are complicated people, it’s… takes some time.

00:01:14.333 --> 00:01:16.375
But normally people are simple and they get it,

00:01:16.583 --> 00:01:19.291
the cool breeze just starts blowing into their hands.

00:01:19.500 --> 00:01:21.959
And that is the breeze of the Holy Ghost.

00:01:22.125 --> 00:01:23.959
REPORTER: Just by holding their hands to the screen at the moment?

00:01:24.125 --> 00:01:25.166
SHRI MATAJI: Just like this. Just like that, yes.

00:01:25.375 --> 00:01:28.959
REPORTER: Well, Your message is self-awareness, self-realism,

00:01:29.125 --> 00:01:31.417
I mean, what exactly does that mean?

00:01:31.625 --> 00:01:34.000
SHRI MATAJI: Self is the reflection of God Almighty in our…

00:01:34.208 --> 00:01:37.542
in the heart. But it resides on top of your head.

00:01:37.750 --> 00:01:39.041
And what is self-realization

00:01:39.250 --> 00:01:42.291
in ordinary words you can say, the real baptism.

00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:44.000
Is the real baptism.

00:01:44.208 --> 00:01:49.333
Means what happens, that your Spirit enters into your awareness,

00:01:49.542 --> 00:01:53.709
into your conscious mind, into your central nervous system,

00:01:53.917 --> 00:01:56.792
so that you start feeling the awareness of the Spirit,

00:01:56.999 --> 00:01:59.625
which is flowing through you as energy.

00:01:59.834 --> 00:02:03.834
This is the energy of the all-pervading Power of God.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:05.583
REPORTER: But I’m sure many people must feel

00:02:05.792 --> 00:02:07.959
that they know themselves perfectly well already,

00:02:08.125 --> 00:02:10.375
without any extra power required.

00:02:10.625 --> 00:02:12.667
SHRI MATAJI: This is a self-opinionated thing.

00:02:12.875 --> 00:02:14.166
But there is a way to find out

00:02:14.375 --> 00:02:16.417
if you know yourself, then you must know

00:02:16.625 --> 00:02:18.208
what are the centres catching in you,

00:02:18.417 --> 00:02:20.667
what are the centres are catching in another person.

00:02:20.875 --> 00:02:22.458
It is the becoming that is important,

00:02:22.667 --> 00:02:24.999
it’s not a mental projection that “I’m such and such.”

00:02:25.208 --> 00:02:27.458
Supposing I say I’m the governor of some place.

00:02:27.667 --> 00:02:29.709
Do I become? No. I must have the powers.

00:02:29.917 --> 00:02:30.999
REPORTER: And You can actually look at another

00:02:31.166 --> 00:02:32.583
person and say what is wrong with that person,

00:02:32.792 --> 00:02:33.709
or feel what is wrong with that person?

00:02:33.917 --> 00:02:36.250
SHRI MATAJI: Yes, I can, I can look at the person and say,

00:02:36.458 --> 00:02:38.250
but others, those who are Sahaja Yogis,

00:02:38.458 --> 00:02:40.417
can just feel it on their fingertips.

00:02:40.625 --> 00:02:41.750
But we talk another language,

00:02:41.959 --> 00:02:44.458
we don’t say “You have cancer,” because that’s not good to say.

00:02:44.667 --> 00:02:47.542
But what we say,“You are catching on this centre or that centre.”

00:02:47.750 --> 00:02:49.667
Supposing somebody is very egoistical.

00:02:49.875 --> 00:02:51.250
Then we don’t say “You are egoistical,”

00:02:51.458 --> 00:02:52.750
we say “You are catching on Agnya,”

00:02:52.959 --> 00:02:54.125
so he doesn’t feel hurt, you know.

00:02:54.333 --> 00:02:55.875
REPORTER: But having identified the problems

00:02:56.041 --> 00:02:57.125
you can also cure them as well.

00:02:57.333 --> 00:02:59.709
SHRI MATAJI: Yes. If we identify the problems,

00:02:59.917 --> 00:03:01.999
we also know how to cure them.

00:03:02.166 --> 00:03:03.834
REPORTER: What happened twenty years ago,

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:06.709
before gurus even were heard of in the Western world?

00:03:06.917 --> 00:03:08.834
We seemed to survive perfectly well without them.

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:11.000
SHRI MATAJI: You see, this is the time of resurrection,

00:03:11.208 --> 00:03:13.041
this is the time of Last Judgment.

00:03:13.250 --> 00:03:16.500
It’s been pointed out by your great poet William Blake,

00:03:16.709 --> 00:03:19.583
who said that a new category of human beings,

00:03:19.792 --> 00:03:22.917
he called them Men of God, will be born on this earth,

00:03:23.125 --> 00:03:25.875
and they will become prophets, and they will have powers

00:03:26.041 --> 00:03:27.125
to make others prophets.

00:03:27.333 --> 00:03:29.709
Of course there has been prophecy also in India

00:03:29.917 --> 00:03:33.625
thousands of years back, that in… this work will start in 1970

00:03:33.834 --> 00:03:35.667
and that many people will get their realization.

00:03:35.875 --> 00:03:36.917
Is already announced.

00:03:37.083 --> 00:03:38.125
REPORTER: And now we are in that time.

00:03:38.333 --> 00:03:39.417
SHRI MATAJI: Yes, that the time has come,

00:03:39.625 --> 00:03:41.041
that’s why these people have taken birth.

00:03:41.291 --> 00:03:44.542
And there are many children who are born realized,

00:03:44.709 --> 00:03:46.041
and you do not know what they are,

00:03:46.250 --> 00:03:48.750
because they have these vibrations and they are different people.

00:03:48.959 --> 00:03:50.417
REPORTER: Mataji, thank you very much indeed.

00:03:50.625 --> 00:03:53.625
SHRI MATAJI: Thank you.
